name: Ambivalence ( alternate poster version )
description:
Ambivalence ( alternate poster version ) on JPEG.  I made this work as an alternative poster version for the latest single from Primata with the same title Ambivalensi , and also as a form of my tribute for the legendary artist Moebius.  For something to be Moebius-like, it has to embrace that psychedelic, dream-like, and mystical dimension.

This #OBJKT is also a gift for those who have collected the Spacewombat X Primata #PrimataXspacewombat collaboration as a form of deep gratitude.  Thank you.

Ambivalence / JPEG / 3300 x 4000 px / 7MB
